  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE STORY</strong></h2><br>Explore the valley of Laywind and unravel a grand mystery. A great incident has set off a chain of events and the ghosts of fallen soldiers now haunt long-dormant lands. A monolithic corporation lurks in the shadows. You are a mysterious unnamed soul whose circumstances remain yet unknown.<br><br>Astra: Era Of Anguish is an RPG prequel set in the GOR3 universe.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><br><u>Old School RPG Combat:</u><br>To-hit roll combat, Your skill point allocation determines how well you can attack and defend yourself. <br><br><u>Character Customization: </u><br>Allocate skill points, and customize your appearance. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111620/extras/e75317dc11f81fc8c4adfb515d653c27.poster.avif?t=1735927183\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111620/extras/e75317dc11f81fc8c4adfb515d653c27.webm?t=1735927183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111620/extras/e75317dc11f81fc8c4adfb515d653c27.mp4?t=1735927183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Open World Exploration:</u><br>Explore a world over 5x the size of Astra. Find sidequests and items; embark on a quest to unravel a grand mystery.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111620/extras/effff74b051570041ae94412b6c56d40.poster.avif?t=1735927183\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111620/extras/effff74b051570041ae94412b6c56d40.webm?t=1735927183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akam